headline: 2 Reasons to Like CDNS and 1 to Stay Skeptical
summary: Over the past six months, Cadence Design Systems’s shares (currently trading at $290.70) have posted a disappointing 15.8% loss, well below the S&P 500’s 6.2% gain. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
